== 市场 ==
某些产品是为了满足高净值人士的需求，例如，[[宅第|豪宅]]，[[遊艇|游艇]]，头等舱机票和[[商務噴射機|私人飞机]]，以及个人雨伞保险，这些[[炫耀性消費|人群会大量消费]][[奢侈品|奢侈品]]和服务。 <ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Conspicuous consumption is over. It's all about intangibles now|url=https://aeon.co/ideas/conspicuous-consumption-is-over-its-all-about-intangibles-now|accessdate=2018-12-24|author=Currid-Halkett, Elizabeth|work=Aeon Ideaslanguage=en|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416174819/https://aeon.co/ideas/conspicuous-consumption-is-over-its-all-about-intangibles-now|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于经济增长使中产阶级能够负担得起历史上昂贵的商品，因此购买趋向于无形产品，例如教育。 截至2017年，特约医疗在美国已成为一种新兴趋势。 <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/03/business/economy/high-end-medical-care.html|title=The Doctor Is In. Co-Pay? $40,000.|author=Schwartz|first=Nelson D.|date=2017-06-03|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-12-24|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525015909/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/03/business/economy/high-end-medical-care.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 银行和金融 ===
大多数全球银行，例如[[桑坦德銀行|桑坦德]]银行，[[巴克莱银行|巴克莱银行]]，[[法國巴黎銀行|法国巴黎银行]]，[[花旗银行|花旗银行]]，[[瑞士信贷集團|瑞士信贷]]，[[德意志银行|德意志银行]]，[[滙豐|汇丰银行]]，[[摩根大通|摩根大通]]和[[瑞银集团|瑞银]]，都有独立的业务部门，其指定团队由专门为超高净值人士提供的客户顾问和产品专家组成。这些客户通常被认为具有类似于机构投资者的特征，因为他们的净资产和当前收入的绝大部分来自[[被动收入|被动收入]]，而不是[[職業|劳动力]]。

=== 杂志 ===
某些杂志，例如''[[Monocle|Monocle]]'' ， <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2017/nov/11/monocle-magazine-apartment-tyler-brule|title=Wealth: ''Monocle'': you've seen the magazine – now buy the apartment|author=Neate, Rupert|date=November 11, 2017|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2018-12-24|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416195258/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2017/nov/11/monocle-magazine-apartment-tyler-brule|dead-url=no}}</ref> ''Robb Report'' ， <ref>{{Cite web|title=Magazines for the mega-rich|url=https://nypost.com/2014/12/08/magazines-for-the-mega-rich/|accessdate=2018-12-24|author=Post Staff Report|date=December 8, 2014|work=New York Post|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416181739/https://nypost.com/2014/12/08/magazines-for-the-mega-rich/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和''Worth等''，都是为高净值受众设计的。

=== 零售 ===
[[賓利|Bentley]] ， [[邁巴赫|Maybach]]和[[劳斯莱斯汽车|Rolls-Royce]]等各个行业的品牌积极瞄准极高净值人士和高净值人士来销售他们的产品。罗尔斯·罗伊斯（Rolls-Royce）研究人员在2006年提出，全球有80,000人属于极高净值人士。 极高净值人士个人“平均拥有8辆汽车和3到4座房产。四分之三的人拥有喷气式飞机，大多数人拥有游艇。” <ref name="HuttonTimes5nov2006">{{Cite news|author=Ray Hutton|date=5 November 2006|title=Rich spurn ultra-luxury cars|publisher=The Sunday Times|location=UK|url=http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/business/article40905.ece|accessdate=10 September 2013|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222152116/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/business/article40905.ece|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

